<br>
388pp = 3-4 good gems from OS.<br>
<br>
(58 ) Group Naltron ( 446hp ) over 4 hours = 48pp ( not including dispells )<br>
<br>
(60 ) Group Marzin ( 700hp ) over 4 hours = 144pp ( not including dispells )<br>
<br>
Aego ( 1100 hp combo ) over 5 hours = 144pp ( not including dispells )<br>
<br>
Group Aego ( 1150 hp combo ) over 5 hours = 96pp ( not including dispells )<br>
<br>
These numbers may vary depending on CHA, but as stated, when purchasing DOTs for 10-12pp apiece it is wise to buff your cha over 120.<br>
<br>
On another note, Enchanters rarely seem to be compensated for RUNE ( Same PeriDOTs ).  This spell, when needed, is cast much more often over the course of the hunt.  Its a fantastic spell, however, due to lack of compensation, not used often on others until people have a guild that needs the enchy to chain RUNE.<br>
<br>
